<div class="title">Water, the Sun, and Love</div>
<div class="substance">AMT & Cannabis</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Raypee&Exact=1">Raypee</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Raypee. "Water, the Sun, and Love: An Experience with AMT & Cannabis (exp20786)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Mar 9, 2007. erowid.org/exp/20786</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
